Description: Marketplace for decorating surfaces
Headquarters Regions: Greater Los Angeles Area, West Coast, Western US
Full Description: Swank is a new marketplace for decorating surfaces.  Swank is seeking to revolutionize the way homeowners, designers and construction pros shop for tile, stone, mosaic and hardwood surfaces.  Using its service, Swank promises that customers will "spend less time driving, and more time choosing". Through their desktop, mobile website and mobile applications, Swank helps construction professionals discover new and unique surfaces at great values that they would likely not find elsewhere. Swank sources merchandise from hundreds of vendors, including emerging brands and smaller boutique vendors, as well as larger national brands.  Swank distinguishes itself by offering what they believe to be the world’s largest centralized selection of affordable surfacing materials.  Swanks platform was developed to provide a shopping experience that delivers entertainment, value and convenience for homeowners and industry pros anytime and anywhere. Swank hopes to be able to provide its vendors with access to a large and highly engaged consumer audience, creating significant brand exposure and revenue opportunities. Many of their existing vendors are small-to-medium sized businesses and may have difficulty reaching a targeted audience of homeowners, designers and construction pros on a broad scale. Using Swanks platform, their vendors can potentially reach a large and targeted audience while also eliminating wholesale, direct sales and marketing costs for the products they sell through Swanks platform, potentially making Swank an attractive channel for them. To best serve their customers and vendors, Swank operates a minimal inventory, intermediary drop-ship model where Swank takes customer orders before they purchase inventory from their vendors. As a result, they are able to offer a much larger selection of products to their customers than local flooring or Big box retailers do, while at the same time generating greater sales for their vendors, who are able to match a broader range of their product supply to actual customer demand. Swanks indicates their customers enjoy the flexibility to purchase home improvement products online with easy product delivery, return guarantee and access to product experts. Swank intends to deliver a reliable and hassle-free experience in an industry known for historically poor customer service.  Swank has been operating in a private beta mode since early February 2014. Swank intends to launch the Swank website and mobile apps to the general public in March of 2014. .................................................................................. Mobile apps Swank IOS apps for iPad and iPhone can be downloaded here: https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/swank-tile-stone-wood-flooring/id799942461?mt=8 Swank Android apps for phones and tablets coming soon.
Founders: Richard Lusk, Ross Mathews, Ryan Rush

Full Description: Founded by renowned fragrance designer Laura Slatkin, Nest New York has become a symbol of exquisite craftsmanship and unique olfactory experiences. In this SEO-optimized post, we’ll take you on a journey through the world of Nest New York, exploring its history, fragrance collections, and the secrets behind its success. The Origin Story Nest New York was born out of Laura Slatkin’s lifelong passion for fragrances and her desire to create something truly exceptional. With a background in interior design and a family deeply rooted in the world of fragrances, Laura embarked on a journey to craft scents that could evoke emotions, memories, and a sense of well-being. The brand’s name, “Nest,” reflects Laura’s vision of creating scents that cocoon you in warmth and comfort, much like a bird nurturing its nest. This commitment to sensory experiences and storytelling through scent is at the heart of Nest New York. Craftsmanship and Sustainability What sets Nest New York apart is its dedication to craftsmanship and sustainability. Each fragrance is carefully crafted using the finest ingredients, resulting in a harmonious blend of natural oils and essences. This commitment to quality ensures that every product from Nest New York is an exquisite work of art. Moreover, Nest New York takes its responsibility towards the environment seriously. The brand has made significant strides in reducing its carbon footprint, using sustainable packaging, and supporting ethical sourcing practices. When you choose Nest New York, you’re not only indulging in luxury but also contributing to a greener future.
